      "value": "<p><b>Source</b> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 20</em>, <em>PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 143</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><b>Cost</b> 90 gp <b>Weight</b> 10 lbs.</p><p><b>Damage</b> 1d6/1d6 (small), 1d8/1d8 (medium); <b>Critical</b> x2; <b>Range</b> -; <b>Type</b> B; <b>Special</b> disarm, double, trip</p><p><b>Category</b> Two-Handed; <b>Proficiency</b> Exotic</p><p><b>Weapon Groups</b> Double; Flails</p><h3>Description</h3><p>A dire flail consists of two spheres of spiked iron dangling from chains at opposite ends of a long haft. This weapon excels at short but powerful strikes, and is typically swung in a constant churning motion. The wielder of a dire flail must have great strength, both to use the weapon effectively and to keep from tiring out.</p>"
